  "source": "// C-style for loop (no range sugar) within a contract.\nseiyaku RangeFor {\n  kotoage fn sum_to(n: int) -> int {\n    let acc = 0;\n    for let i = 0; i < n; i++ {\n      acc = acc + i;\n    }\n    return acc;\n  }\n}\n",
